    {
      "provider_name": "DermSurgery Associates",
      "location_city": "Houston",
      "location_state": "TX",
      "method_used": "Q-Switch",
      "review_text": "I had a very disappointing experience at this dermatologist’s office. I arrived about 10 minutes late to my appointment, but no one informed me that this would significantly impact my wait time. I ended up sitting in the waiting room for an hour and 20 minutes, during which I watched multiple patients who arrived after me get called in before me.\n\nThe staff only apologized after I went up to the front desk to ask what was going on. At that point, I was so frustrated that I decided to leave without even seeing the doctor.\n\nOverall, the lack of communication and the excessive wait time made this visit incredibly frustrating. I won’t be returning.",
      "star_rating": 1,
      "review_date": "3 months ago",
      "reviewer_name": "Deepika Gupta",
      "verified_source": "Google",
      "_place_title": "DermSurgery Associates – Main - Dermatology",
      "review_date_resolved": "2026-01-02"
