    {
      "provider_name": "DermSurgery Associates",
      "location_city": "Houston",
      "location_state": "TX",
      "method_used": "Q-Switch",
      "review_text": "A small basal cell carcinoma was found just below my eyebrow after a biopsy was analyzed. Dr. Conner Chan referred me to  Dermsurgery Associates in Bellaire, TX. This was my first experience with cancer and the term MOHS surgery. I was nervous. When I called the office, they were kind, patient and informative . Prior to the appointment, we visited the offices which are very easy to find and very nice.  My doctor was Dr.Nhan Nguyen. He and his assistant were personable and thorough. I had no pain at all. I highly recommend Dr. Nguyen and this location.",
      "star_rating": 5,
      "review_date": "4 months ago",
      "reviewer_name": "Jesus & Donna Balderas",
      "verified_source": "Google",
      "_place_title": "DermSurgery Associates – Main - Dermatology",
