    {
      "provider_name": "DermSurgery Associates",
      "location_city": "Houston",
      "location_state": "TX",
      "method_used": "Q-Switch",
      "review_text": "I called to schedule a consultation with Dr. Kromberg and specifically asked if there was a consult fee. I was told there wasn’t one. My appointment was scheduled for 10:45 am, and I arrived at 10:30. However, I wasn’t seen until 11:30, and the appointment itself lasted no more than 10 minutes.\n\nAfterward, I was informed there was a $150 consult fee. I explained that I was told over the phone there was no charge, but the staff said they weren’t sure who I spoke with and that I still needed to pay.\n\nI’m sharing this so others are aware - be sure to confirm any fees in writing beforehand. I feel misled and disappointed to have been charged $150 for something I was told would be free. Transparency and clear communication about costs are very important, and unfortunately, that was lacking here.",
      "star_rating": 1,
      "review_date": "5 months ago",
